         SPELL=qsstv
         VERSION=5.1a
          SOURCE=$SPELL-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/$SPELL-$VERSION
   SOURCE_URL[0]=http://users.pandora.be/on1mh/download/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://users.pandora.be/on1mh/
         ENTERED=20011212
         UPDATED=20011212
      MAINTAINER=jasonflatt@wizard.com
           SHORT="Slow-scan tv and fax program for hams"
cat << EOF

Application which uses /dev/dsp to receive and transmit slow scan television.
Uses the Qt library.  Supports Martins 1/2, Scottie 1/2, Wraase SC2 180,
Robot36, VIS -code and Sync/Non-Synced operation.  Transmit modes are Martin
1 and 2.  Can store images on your harddisk.  Nice gui.

EOF
